  <brief_title>Drug Compliance and Quality of Life in Patients With Heart Failure Dosed With Either Once-daily or Twice-daily Coreg</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective, Randomized, Controlled Assessment of Once-Daily Controlled Release COREG CR vs Twice-Daily COREG Immediate Release(IR)on Measures of Compliance and Quality of Life in Patients With Heart Failure and Left Ventricular Systolic Dysfunction</official_title>
  <sponsors>
